    safetyNote: "Start dexamethasone IMMEDIATELY on clinical suspicion - do not delay for MRI. Pre-treatment neurological status is the strongest predictor of outcome",
    distractorRationales: ["The epidural mass with cancer history makes metastatic disease far more likely than disc herniation", "Transverse myelitis is inflammatory, not mass-related, and has different MRI appearance", "Compression fracture does not cause an epidural mass compressing the cord"],
